'''标致408'''（'''Peugeot 408'''）或者称为[[东风汽车公司|东风]]标致408，是[[标致|标致]]与[[东风汽车公司|东风汽车公司]]于2010年1月25日在北京推出的一個[[紧凑型轿车|-{zh-hans:紧凑型; zh-hant:小型;}-汽車]]（Compact Car）车系<ref name="pressrelease1">{{cite web|url=http://www.peugeot.com/en/news/2010/1/25/408-in-beijing.aspx|title=408 in Beijing|publisher=[[Peugeot|Peugeot]]|date=2010-01-25|accessdate=2010-04-13|archive-date=2012-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120304004401/http://www.peugeot.com/en/news/2010/1/25/408-in-beijing.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。自同年4月8日开始在[[中国|中国]]市场销售<ref name="pressrelease2">{{cite web|url=http://www.peugeot.com/en/news/2010/4/9/commercial-launch-of-the-peugeot-408-in-china.aspx|title=Commercial launch of the Peugeot 408 in China|publisher=[[Peugeot|Peugeot]]|date=2010-04-09|accessdate=2010-04-13|archive-date=2012-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120503204043/http://www.peugeot.com/en/news/2010/4/9/commercial-launch-of-the-peugeot-408-in-china.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。目前正在销售的是其第二代产品。

[[File:Peugeot_408_II_002_China_2015-04-13.jpg|right]]
虽然该车系名为“标致408”，但并非[[标致407|标致407]]的继任者，而是[[标致308|标致308]]的加长轴距版[[轿车|轿车]]<ref>[http://www.autocarbe.com/peugeot/peugeot-408-official-pictures-and-details-of-the-308-sedan-for-china/ Peugeot 408: Official pictures and details of the 308 sedan for China] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110707191853/http://www.autocarbe.com/peugeot/peugeot-408-official-pictures-and-details-of-the-308-sedan-for-china/ |date=2011-07-07 }} - Autocarbe, 26 Jan 2010</ref>。该车系主要针对中国这样的[[新兴市场|新兴市场]]国家，并且不會進軍[[欧洲|欧洲]]<ref>[http://www.peugeot.com/en/news/2010/4/9/commercial-launch-of-the-peugeot-408-in-china.aspx Commercial launch of the Peugeot 408 in China] {{Wayback|url=http://www.peugeot.com/en/news/2010/4/9/commercial-launch-of-the-peugeot-408-in-china.aspx |date=20120503204043 }} - Peugeot Press Release, 8 Apr 2010</ref>。在欧洲市场，标致407的继任者为[[标致508|标致508]]。

